Note: This document makes heavy use of OS 3.1 @{amigaguide} commands.@{par}

@endnode

@node "Requirements" "Requirements"
@{par}
  @{b}@{u}Requirements@{uu}@{ub}@{par}

ImageButton.mcc requires at least version 3.0 of MUI (V11).@{par}
It is recommended that you always use the latest version of MUI.@{par}

@endnode

@node "History" "History"
@{par}
  @{b}@{u}History@{uu}@{ub}@{par}

11.0, 13-Apr-1997:@{par}
@{lindent 4}  - first version of ImageButton.mcc@{lindent 0}@{par}

11.1, 15-Apr-1997:@{par}
@{lindent 4}  - the label can now be at all positions around the image: left, right,
above or below@{lindent 0}@{par}
@{lindent 4}  - Image specifications can now be used as an image, too@{lindent 0}@{par}
@{lindent 4}  - reworked autodocs@{lindent 0}@{par}

11.2, 14-Jul-1997:@{par}
@{lindent 4}  - did some internal improvements and cleanup@{lindent 0}@{par}

@endnode

